org.geppetto.core.recordings

Class GeppettoRecordingCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.geppetto.core.recordings.GeppettoRecordingCreator

  • public class GeppettoRecordingCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates HDF5 Recordings file. API can take different array datasets and single values for integers, doubles and floats.
    Author:
    Jesus R Martinez (jesus@metacell.us)
